{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act17side_level_act17side_st08","storyGroup":"act17side","storySort":17,"storyDependence":"act17side_level_act17side_07_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"SN-ST-8","storyName":"指挥大厅","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act17side/level_act17side_st08","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act17side_08","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":15,"next":17,"characters":["歌蕾蒂娅","圣徒卡门","古怪的教徒","极境","负责拷问的教徒","蒂亚戈","？？？","乌尔比安","船长阿方索","大副","最后的骑士","幽灵鲨","斯卡蒂"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"dialog","id":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":2},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_bg_27_g23_goldenboat_pass.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":7},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","fadetime":"1","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":10,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":11},{"type":"showitem","image":"item_act27_1","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","offsetx":"0","width":"200","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":13},{"type":"hideitem","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":15},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"这里。","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"（他引我来到这里，随后隐去了气味。看来他在陆地上学会了不少手段。）","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":22},{"type":"text","text":"歌蕾蒂娅环顾四周。","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"她知道，有一个曾经的友人就在这附近盯着她。","id":24},{"type":"text","text":"但她没有犹豫，也没有时间犹豫。她必须尽快得到关于这艘船的全部秘密，她必须......带着这些秘密，重回阿戈尔。","id":25},{"type":"text","text":"她想回到家园。她想帮助自己的家园，对抗灾祸。","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"歌蕾蒂娅看着手里的钥匙。","id":27},{"type":"text","text":"她打开了宝库的大门。","id":28},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_dooropen","id":29},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":31},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":32},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":34},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_bg_27_g16_lighthouse_street.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":35},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":36},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_plot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":37,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$burningloop1","loop":"true","channel":"fire","id":38},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":39},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#6$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"焚烧这些溟痕很费功夫，我真该谢谢凯尔希和那只漆黑的生物。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"溟痕吞噬不掉这片礁石。很遗憾。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"但这也只是万千形态中的一种，你没有听过预言，你不会理解。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"预言？不过是未知生物的信徒，一群逃避者，难道还需要未来？","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"fire","fadetime":"4","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"先知与你们不同。她从不描述虚伪的未来，从不做无法实践的许诺。","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"她只说，只说千万片巨鳞将汇成一体，飞向深空。只说大海将被光芒涂抹，此消彼长，永不干涸。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"只说生命的死亡和消逝都将融为一体，届时，连这片虚假的群星都遮蔽不住生命的光芒。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"我们将生存在那样一个生态中。我们皆是壮美循环的一部分。生命诞生，生命奉献，生命寻求价值，生命消逝，周而复始。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#7$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"听上去，不过是某种源石技艺给你们看到的幻觉罢了。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#7$1","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"将伊比利亚逼到如此境地，数百万生灵涂炭，这也是壮美循环的一部分吗？","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"你理解什么？！族群从不将个体的死当做“结束”，生命在结束后仍属于壮美循环的一部分！","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"你愤怒，你焦躁，你还只是个人类啊，异端。","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"......我不会被你抓住，审判官。我知道你的源石技艺，可恨的法术。我们都做好了奉献的准备。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"你将永远无法触及先知，就像你抓不住时间，时间从你的指尖流逝！","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":69},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":70},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_fish_howl","id":71},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_457_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_457_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":72},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"大审判官！格兰法洛的所有人都对你们积怨已久！惩戒军靠近不了这里，现在你孤身一人！","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"古怪的教徒","text":"你逃不掉的！","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"......逃？","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#6$1","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"我们在这里，难道是为了费口舌争辩，正义与邪恶的吗？","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_avg_npc_447_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":83},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_bg_bg_ibbar.png","width":"1","height":"1","fadetime":"0","id":84},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":86},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#10$1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"哈啊......哈啊......","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4d/Avg_avg_npc_450_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"他什么都不说，愚蠢的伊比利亚人......","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"那只黑色怪物一定有弱点，它坚硬无比，还能轻易烧毁溟痕......它究竟是什么？！","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"如果再不得到些情报，等惩戒军突破了包围网，我们就——","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#1$1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"——就失败了？","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_npc_450_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#1$1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"哈哈......就凭你们是对付不了凯尔希医生和那位审判官阁下的。你们已经输了。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_npc_450_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"住口！","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"我要把你——等等，你在做什么？！","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"你的杖为什么有动静！？你做了什么？","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#1$1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"你们似乎太关注你们的海洋动物了......哦，你们是不是都不懂什么叫“源石技艺”？","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_npc_450_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#1$1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"太脱离现实生活可不好——","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_npc_450_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":105},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#10$1","id":106},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","id":107},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"咕哈——","id":109,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4d/Avg_avg_npc_450_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":110},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"自以为是的家伙——！你以为我们什么都没准备？为了把你们这些和审判庭同流合污的人一网打尽，我们筹备了多久！","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":113},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":115},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","fadetime":"1","id":116},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"别相信他的故弄玄虚，他在这个小镇躲藏了几个月，他是个间谍，精通通讯手段的间谍。","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_451_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"也许我们的位置已经暴露了。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_451_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"......间谍，间谍，我们之中一定早就潜伏了审判庭的间谍！","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我知道你们的存在，是因为你们不加掩饰，我和阿玛雅走得很近。但审判庭不同，他们确实怀着恶意对待格兰法洛，如果他们想藏......","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_451_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我们毕竟只是世代为工的工人，我们怎么发现呢？","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_451_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"那就把他丢出去喂给同胞们吧。溟痕蔓延的速度在减缓，我们需要更多养分，阻拦惩戒军。","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"然后，我们也应当想办法离开。","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_453_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"好。我来带路，没有人比我更熟悉格兰法洛，过去我们留下了不少暗道和地下仓库......","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_451_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#2$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极境","text":"蒂亚戈，你不该这么做。","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_450_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我们才认识多久？你来教我怎么做，空喊口号的卫道士？","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_451_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"站起来，走，你会变成海的一部分。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_451_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":139},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":140},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":141},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":142},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_bg_27_g25_goldenboat_core.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":143},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":145},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":146,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"（原来如此。）","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"（源石能源与阿戈尔科技的结合，更坚固的穹顶，陆地移动城市的应用模式，源石技艺的拓展性。）","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"（这就是科学院的天才眼中的大地。几十年时间，足够他做到这些......）","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"（但是......）","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"但是还不够。","id":156},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#2","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":160},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","fadetime":"2","id":162},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","id":163},{"type":"dialog","id":164},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":167},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_27_i35.png","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","x":"-150","y":"80","id":168},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleTo":"0.8","duration":"80","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","block":"false","id":169},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"即使不依靠与陆地的交流，阿戈尔依然能做到。些微技术融合，成为不了反败为胜的关键。","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"果然......是你。","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"这不是一件好事，乌尔比安。","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"站稳了，你若是多走一步，我会贯穿你，我曾经的战友。","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"斯卡蒂一度认为，深海猎人只剩她最后一人。连她都觉得你死了，你却还活着。","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你很敏锐，执政官歌蕾蒂娅。","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"这种场合似乎没必要在意繁文缛节，执政官乌尔比安。","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"很久没听人这么称呼你，感到怀念了吗？","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我们相识很久了。没有归队的猎人意味着什么，你最清楚。","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我处决的人不比你少。而我现在依然可以保证，如果幸存者中有人堕入深渊，我会在他们听见那歌声前，把他们悬挂在干燥的礁石上。","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"那么现在呢？你身上有它们的气味，你与它们同流合污。","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"别骗自己。歌蕾蒂娅，你对他人严厉，但你对自己更甚。","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"难道在陆地上徘徊，已经让你享受上折磨自己的感觉了？","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"猎人，如果你的回答不让我满意，我会杀死你。","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"歌蕾蒂娅，大部分事情在脱离你的掌控，我必须从另一个角度解决问题。","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"什么事情？","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我......和你们一样。在陆地上生活了一小段时间。","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但是，我看见了些别的东西。你理解陆上文明了吗？不，你不用回答，傲慢的歌蕾蒂娅。","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"陆地文明为了生存，开发源石。源石带给他们机遇与希望，也带给他们新的灾难，时至今日，他们仍旧无法彻底解析源石的原理。","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我看过很多惨剧......他们称之为“天灾”。他们愚昧，无知，弱小，可他们的灭亡与挣扎依旧触目惊心。","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......阿戈尔，与他们毫无区别。","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你过去不是个软弱的人。","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"不。我不是在谈论感性的话题。","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我是说，阿戈尔为了生存而惊动了海洋，海洋吞噬阿戈尔，然后又诞生了我们。","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我们是畸形斗争的产物。我们不能从源头解决问题，我们就无法解决问题。","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......你看到了什么？乌尔比安。你看到了什么，让你放弃血的馈赠，放弃我们并肩作战的情谊？","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"“神殿”。如果是那些令人作呕的教徒，他们一定会如此称呼。","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你对他们的熟络只会削减我对你的信任。","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但这个词，很贴切。","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你知道阿戈尔曾经在海洋深处发现过什么。即使你不是专业的历史学家，通识教育也该涉及这一部分。","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"数千年前，我们抵达海洋的中心。在那里，我们发现了原点。文明的原点。","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......据我所知，歌蕾蒂娅。","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"在祂......和那些海嗣的巢穴的最深处......最深处。","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我看见了，“建筑”，不，即使请来阿戈尔最伟大的科学执政官，他们也无法解释我所见到的。","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我无法深入，我受伤太重。沸腾的血液，震耳欲聋的噪声，但我还是感到了——","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......什么？","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"——那里有复数的祂。","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"............","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"那么......这似乎，不成为你离队的理由。你更该带回这一情报。","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"千万哀嚎归于一点的时候，那些尚未出生的海嗣，它们在形态各异的胚胎中低吟着同一个名字。","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......Ishar-mla。","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"或者说，斯卡蒂。","id":217},{"type":"dialog","id":218},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":219},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":221},{"type":"image","id":222},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_bg_27_g21_goldenboat_deck.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":223},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$batmeeting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_batmeeting_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":224,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":225},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sea","volume":"0.6","loop":"true","channel":"sea","id":226},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":227},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#5$1","fadetime":"1","id":228},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"......跳进海里了吗？","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#5$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"它还会上来，我们再等一会。","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#5$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"哦，谁让我们是它的“同族”呢，真可怜。","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_452_1#1$1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"大副","text":"......！","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_avg_npc_452_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#1$1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"......唔。我看见了，浪头在不自然地粉碎，它就像旋风或是海市蜃楼一样，多不自然的奇观。","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#9$1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"啐，今天真是热闹啊。自从小杰米和厨子死后，再没这么热闹过了。","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":241},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":242},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_footstep_stonestep","volume":"0.6","id":243},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","fadetime":"2","id":244},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"......唔。","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"石榴......花。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#9$1","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"......骑士。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"我还以为还会有一些时日见不到你。你重来我的船上，难道是贪恋家乡的气味吗？你还没彻底疯掉吗？","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"......","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"骑士只是默默盯着阿方索。","id":254},{"type":"text","text":"但很快，他把目光放回了海洋。阿方索随之望去，在时间愈发模糊的岁月里，日月已经失去意义。","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#9$1","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"你还在狩猎巨浪吗？","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"......","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#9$1","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"但愿这些怪物的血还没有让你得到永生。这样你总有一天会迎接溺亡，溺亡是幸福的。","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"......","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#9$1","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"今天......风不大。","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"......浪涛，是海洋的，呼吸。","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"它还没有，停止呼吸。","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"还没有，死亡。","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"就像，地上的，怪物。吞食，毁灭。","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_446_1#9$1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"船长阿方索","text":"地上的怪物。","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_446_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"文明！","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"sea","fadetime":"2","id":278},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":279},{"type":"dialog","id":280},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":281},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":282},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_bg_27_g23_goldenboat_pass.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":283},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":285,"musicid":4},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#11$1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"斯卡蒂。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/64/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#2","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"嗯？","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_char_263_skadi_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#11$1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"我又想起来一些事情。我们......是怎么活下来的？","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/64/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"你又是怎么活下来的？","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/64/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#9","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"记不清细节了，我们砍杀，无休止地砍杀，然后祂......","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#11$1","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"我是说，呃，如果那时候，它们的整个族群要我们死，我们能活下来吗？","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/64/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#9","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"换言之，阿戈尔也不知道我们活下来了。","id":300,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#2","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"他们没办法知道。","id":302,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_char_263_skadi_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#13$1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"是剑鱼说要来这艘船的？","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#2","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"是。她说这艘船有办法带我们回家。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_char_263_skadi_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#13$1","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"唔，这像是阿戈尔的工艺，造船师......布雷奥甘，没印象的名字。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#9","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......过去你也不记那些科学院的人名。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"你不也是？","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......能这样和你说话，我安心许多。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你真的回来了，劳伦缇娜，你不会再离我们而去了吧？","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"呵呵，有必要说这么肉麻吗？我以前也和你们在一起，只是稍微迷糊了一点，扮一扮乖巧的修女，我也挺喜欢那样的感觉的。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#6$1","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"哦，不过这一身是队长让罗德岛的朋友们帮我订做的？她竟然知道具体的尺寸。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......实际上，你甚至还长高了一点。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"你也知道？","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#9","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我......我只是帮了忙。二队长说她信不过陆上人的品味。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"品味？呵呵......","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"其实我们都知道她本人并不在意这些事情。谢谢她在这样的细节上总是这么到位。","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"她说你喜欢长裙，以前就是，我也有印象。不过......我很少做这种......裁缝活儿。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#6$1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"嗯......","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"......啊，这些符号，这些阿戈尔文字，我们一起写上去的。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"写着你的事情，歌蕾蒂娅的事情，我的事情。写着我们的阿戈尔，写着......我们的家乡。","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"这是谁的主意？总不会是我自己的吧？","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我们三个人的主意。","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#6$1","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"那款式呢？","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......剑鱼挑的。","id":342,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#7$1","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"难为她了。","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#2","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我们得专注于战斗。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_char_263_skadi_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"我知道，但是我也没有放弃过在狩猎前整理仪容，不是吗？","id":348,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"斯卡蒂，你知道当我从一片混沌中想起自己是谁的时候，第一件想到的事情是什么吗？","id":349,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#2","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"什么？","id":351,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_char_263_skadi_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"是重新审视当下的自己，和那个遥远的、清晰记忆的彼岸的自己，有多大差别。","id":353,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"虽然上一次当一个乖乖修女，我不算讨厌——","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"可现在这样由值得信任的同胞来决定的模样，更得我心。你能明白我的心情吗？","id":355,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"唔......肯定比你在盐风城的那个罐子里清醒过来时要好不少。","id":357,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#7$1","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"哈哈，说得对。","id":359,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"所以，现在，我们要说服我们的船长先生，对吧？","id":361,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"交给我吧。","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":363},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":364},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":366},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_bg_27_g25_goldenboat_core.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":367},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":368},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_plot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":369,"musicid":5},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"这不可能。不......","id":371,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"Ishar-mla。","id":373,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"当我随着巨物的尸骸沉入海沟，在寻常阿戈尔人都无法承受的压力之中，我看见了以前从未见过之物。","id":375,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"歌蕾蒂娅，你知道阿戈尔为什么与陆地绝缘。你知道源石、天灾无法侵袭阿戈尔的种种推论。","id":377,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"它们大多被证明是正确的。海洋就像一个培养皿，养育，并呵护着阿戈尔的纯洁。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但是......如果我们引以为傲的文明，才是附着于某些巨物之上的霉菌呢？","id":381,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你过去就善于质疑，这让你在诸多领域都有所建树，开创性的建树。但污蔑阿戈尔？你变得太多，我都认不出来了。","id":383,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"而且，话题不该扯那么远。你对斯卡蒂的猜测......你对你自己的猎人，给出了最残酷的指控。","id":385,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"“海嗣”只是一个笼统的命名。你知道，它们的生命形式更加复杂。","id":387,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你不是没有担心过，斯卡蒂也许会成为其中更高级的那一个，对吧？","id":389,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我担心你先选错了道路。","id":391,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"一队，四队，死在了途中，一头一尾，为我们创造了突破的机会。","id":393,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你们，二队，留在巢穴附近。那很难用“巢穴”描述，我们仿佛进入了一个巨大的整体，我们是渺小的病菌。","id":395,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"但病菌也能杀死一个健康的人。","id":397,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"所以我们成功了。我们自以为成功了。","id":399,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我只是，与祂的尸骸一同沉眠。血，如果那发光的流体是血的话，洒满我全身，将我包裹。","id":401,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但我只是与祂的尸体一起睡了个好觉。我躲藏在祂的空壳中，靠着祂残留的血肉，直到周围的声音全都平静。","id":403,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"那斯卡蒂呢？是她战斗到最后一刻。","id":405,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":407,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"那不是一次正常的“杀死”。那不是“捕食”。那是一次“喂食”，族群的喂食。","id":409,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你的猜测正确也谬误。你以为所有深海猎人都会失控，变成海嗣？不。斯卡蒂不会。","id":411,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你已经明白了。直面过祂，在那条海沟里沉沦浮起的我们，都明白。","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你是说......","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"发生任何问题，我们就得杀死她。","id":417,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":418},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"她是你的猎人。","id":419,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"而你，甚至没有为你刻意的隐瞒和背叛做出解释。你却要我相信你的猜测？","id":421,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我不喜欢你保持沉默的习惯。也许我需要夺走你的行动能力，将你带回阿戈尔。","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"很遗憾，终于有一位执政官在抗争中堕落，这也许会损害士气。","id":427,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你做不到的。","id":429,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"歌蕾蒂娅。在你为自己的变化而焦虑的时候，你还要号称自己代表阿戈尔吗？","id":431,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这是一个机会。我不奢求你的理解与帮助，但我们中总有人得抓住这个机会。","id":433,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"揭开真相，才有活路。","id":435,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#2","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"这与你现在的行为有何联系？","id":437,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你来找船，我来找布雷奥甘，那个阿戈尔人。","id":439,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我已经有所突破，布雷奥甘的证据佐证了我所见的。他很了不起。在那个年份，在那个条件下，得出了与我无异的结论。","id":441,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":442},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你手边的那些——你已经明白了，那些才是真正有价值的东西。陆地上不会有人理解，所以他死去得孤独。","id":443,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"并非完全没有人理解。但是......","id":445,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"“但是”。坚定如你，强势如你，说过几次“但是”？","id":447,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我们是同僚，我们共同设计了这场战争，我们该更相互信赖一些。","id":449,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"最后劝你，别回阿戈尔，还太早，太危险。我们还有很多事情没有弄清楚，回去也是徒劳，你也不知道阿戈尔究竟变成了什么样。","id":451,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"留在陆地上。真有什么意外，你说得对——她是我的猎人。","id":453,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我会承担责任。","id":455,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":456},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":457},{"type":"text","text":"歌蕾蒂娅还想说些什么。","id":458},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_ship_creak","volume":"0.6","id":459},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rockfall","volume":"1","id":460},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":461},{"type":"text","text":"但转头间，巨大的裂响传遍了房间的每个角落，随之而来的是猛烈的晃动，那满桌的真理撒落在地上，在歌蕾蒂娅眼中显得格外烫眼。","id":462},{"type":"text","text":"“海神”。","id":463},{"type":"text","text":"在总战争设计师们提出深海猎人这一计划前，在深海猎人奔赴巢穴前，布雷奥甘选用了如今陆上的愚信徒们才会痴迷的称呼。","id":464},{"type":"text","text":"他想将灾难的本源研究透彻。他在陆地上找到了最后一块拼图。","id":465},{"type":"dialog","id":466},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":467},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_footstep_stonestep","volume":"0.6","id":468},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","fadetime":"2","id":469},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"......钥匙......我......小麦的气息......家园？家园支援我。家人支援我。","id":471,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_448_1#1$1","id":472},{"type":"dialogue","name":"最后的骑士","text":"直到我，粉碎大海。","id":473,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_448_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":474},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":475},{"type":"text","text":"两个猎人看向沉吟的骑士。","id":476},{"type":"text","text":"歌蕾蒂娅握紧了手里的钥匙。","id":477},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":478},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......那就看看这个怪物，仔细看看。似人非人，连族群都不接纳他。","id":479,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"日复一日地寻找巨浪，击碎巨浪，永无止境，徒劳无功。","id":481,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_445_1#1$1","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"和我们一样。","id":483,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_445_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":484},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":485},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":486},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":487}],"characters":["歌蕾蒂娅","圣徒卡门","古怪的教徒","极境","负责拷问的教徒","蒂亚戈","？？？","乌尔比安","船长阿方索","大副","最后的骑士","幽灵鲨","斯卡蒂"]}